les were collected during 2007.</p> <ul class="spatial hide"><li>153.06,-27.61 153.1,-27.61 153.1,-27.65 153.06,-27.65 153.06,-27.61</li></ul><span class="spatial_center hide">153.08,-27.63</span><br><span class="key hide">shuker.13</span></div></td><td><p class="datePublished">09-10-2012</p><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="show"></a><div id="metabutton" class="expand" style="display: none;"><a target="_blank" href="http://portal-dev.tern.org.au/soil-characteristics-physical-and-chemical-in-karawatha-forest-park-shuker13" class="greenGradient smallRoundedCorners viewmeta">View Metadata</a></div></td></tr></tbody><tbody><tr><td><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="pin2">34</a></td><td><h2><a href="javascript:void(0);">Lizard assemblage in Karawatha Forest Park</a></h2><div id="metadesc" class="expand" style="display: none;"><p style="height: 48px;">Lizard assemblage for 33 plots at Karawatha Forest, determined from pitfall trapping and visual encounter surveys.
